main.java.animals

Class Animal

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.animals.Animal
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Chicken, Cow, Pig

    public abstract class Animal
extends java.lang.Object
    Animals are purchased from the store and are held in the farm. They must be fed regularly and can be harvested from daily to receive product items.
    Version:
    1.0, May 2020.
    Author:
    Daniel Felgate, He Zheng Jing Rui
    See Also:
    Farm.animals, Store

        public void sleep()
        Called at the end of each day for all animals. Decreases hunger and determines whether the animal becomes sick. If the animal is starving it will die. Resets harvested to false.
